<div class="step-content">

<h4>The On-Ramp â” �™ DEX Pipeline</h4>

<p>Buy $SOL on Coinbase or Kraken via ACH (free deposits, tight spreads). Withdraw to your Phantom wallet. Trade meme coins on Jupiter and Raydium. This is the standard workflow for 80% of Solana meme coin traders. Keeps fiat handling on regulated platforms while executing trades on fast, low-fee DEXs.</p>

</div>

</div>



<div class="step-card">

