<h4>CEX Limit Orders for Large Positions</h4>

<p>For building or exiting large positions in established tokens ($BONK, $WIF, $DKING), use Kraken's limit order book. Set your buy order at a specific price and let it fill over hours or days with minimal slippage. Transfer to your DEX wallet for meme-to-meme swaps once you've accumulated your base position.</p>

</div>

</div>



<div class="step-card">

<div class="step-num">3</div>

<div class="step-content">

<h4>DEX Sniping â” �™ CEX Profit-Taking</h4>

<p>Use Jupiter to snipe new token launches at the earliest possible second. Once your position has 5x-10x'd and the token starts appearing on Coinbase/Kraken radar, take profits on the CEX where liquidity is deeper and limit orders protect against flash crashes. This is how professional meme coin traders de-risk their exits.</p>

</div>

</div>



<div class="highlight-box">

<p><strong> Power User Setup:</strong> Create two Solana wallets. Wallet A - a Phantom wallet connected to Jupiter for active meme coin trading. Wallet B - a Ledger-protected Solflare wallet for long-term holdings and CEX withdrawals. Never connect Wallet B to any dApp. Transfer profits from Wallet A to Wallet B weekly. This setup combines DEX speed with cold-storage security.</p>

</div>



